Enemies can either be melee or ranged based, their movement is determined by type.

Melee enemies will always try to move towards the player.
If they come into contact with the player, they will deal damage and play an animation.
All melee damage(done by and against player) will cause small knockback

Ranged enemies will move to a select distance and try to maintain it.
At this range they will strafe around short distances in random directions to try to dodge attacks.
They will always fire if they are within range of their attacks.

Players will attack with spells
They can have 3 spells active at one time.
Mouse 1 and 2 will be bound to the players standard spells.
Spacebar will be used for an "ultimate" spell.
